{"tid":910964,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果離婚要罰重款，可唔可以降低離婚率？","createTime":"2018-11-21T14:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T16:38:38.000Z","uid":204700,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdee2e824a7dd69df368a5d052619975f5303f0","tid":910964,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"現代離婚太容易，好多夫妻遇到問題就輕言離婚。<br />\n其實根本無咁嚴重，可能雙方再協調下再溝通多啲或者去見一見婚姻輔導都可以解決到。<br />\n好多都係一時意氣，又唔肯認輸，唔想認衰先離婚。<br />\n<br />\n如果離婚要重罰，例如雙方都要繳交自己一年嘅薪金出黎，<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以有效降低離婚率令多啲夫妻走得更長？<br />\n<br />\n正評可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負評唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論 請發表你嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cecc608e22b84e2aa69803f79b0cab314534e1e","tid":910964,"uid":53466,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd7d62ff6e98bdc4db566dbbf2a5f51d80763ff9","tid":910964,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"8cecc608e22b84e2aa69803f79b0cab314534e1e","tid":910964,"uid":53466,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果係雙方都要繳交呢"},{"pid":"0e49881c24eb832f5318bb3774a72e292be0b46b","tid":910964,"uid":119028,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"有西用咩 冇感情係埋一齊都冇意思<br />\n用錢黎綁住跟本解決唔到問題"},{"pid":"f4a4f21e69e4ed9ff2fd5a1ea6fb167a614d1d32","tid":910964,"uid":29041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"女多數冇做野"},{"pid":"11e93b1f12793463aa79214b9cdebcbcbd787ff7","tid":910964,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f4d994e9345bceb19b6ed7049947c470829881","tid":910964,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0